creator: BeToBe
descriptionHtml:
Awork is a first ever Georgian Job-Seeker application, that helps people to find proper jobs based on their preferred locations, from search to apply and simplifies entire process of finding a new job.

Why Awork?

- A wide selection of new job openings every day;
- Personalization, to suggest vacancies based on your experience and interests.
- Job feed based on your location;
- Upload your CV and use it when submitting the application;
- Use various filters to find a job with your preferred requirements;
- Swipe Up – Submit your Application Within a second;
- Swipe Right – Save the vacancy for later submission;
- Swipe Left – No interest? Skip it easily;

Searching for a Job?

Download the Awork App, upload your CV and start applying!

If you are enjoying Awork, please take a moment and rate us on the App Store. Thanks for your support!
